title: Making a premade for Invasion Onslaught star guardian quests
body:
Hi everyone!
I want to make a premade team of 5 to do all the onslaught quests. We will start with the easier ones (Old/New Horizon & No Utility/Mage/Marksman). After we finish them we can try to get an A or even an S rank. I already have the A rank but I still need the S. 

Please reply here if you wish to join or fell free to add me ingame (Kristalyszuz - EUNE).
